Read AGENTS.md at the repository root before doing anything else.

AGENTS.md is the single source of truth for this project: stack choices,
folder structure, naming conventions, commit format, and explicit "never do"
rules. Every constraint there applies to you.

If a request would require deviating from AGENTS.md (e.g. introducing a
new framework, modifying protected paths, bypassing prompt versioning),
stop and ask the human first.

Protected paths — do not edit without explicit instruction:
- packages/agent/src/loop.ts
- packages/agent/src/prompts/
- packages/agent/src/retrieval/

Stack choices are decided. Do not substitute alternatives without an ADR.
